{"tid":975697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【所以話】台女被騙玩蒙眼性愛失身　騙徒無事男友罪成","createTime":"2019-01-10T00:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T00:36:15.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5e06b0f8d87839d7b85ce9e7a71bdbd91f31fcc9","tid":975697,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:20:27.000Z","msg":"台女被騙玩蒙眼性愛失身　騙徒無事男友罪成<br />\n<br />\n台灣法官的判案準則，經常令人摸不着頭腦。台北一名楊姓男子，得知女友受騙遭到性侵後，帶武器怒毆張姓騙徒，雙方事後互告性侵和傷害罪。惟檢方認定，張男未以暴力手段逼女方發生性關係，未構成性侵，但楊男傷人一事就證據確鑿。台北地方法院周二（8日）判處楊男傷害罪成，需接受拘役40日，可易科罰金。<br />\n<br />\n這宗匪夷所思的案件發生在2017年7月，住在台北的張男認識案中女子後，得知對方住在高雄，與男友分隔兩地、不常聯絡，於是假冒對方男友，每日傳短訊噓寒問暖。同年8月5日，張約女方旅行，並提議她脫光衣服、全程矇上眼睛，雙方來一場刺激的矇眼性愛遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n女方同意張男的要求，當晚赤裸身體並戴上眼罩，將門鎖打開在房間等候。張男成功登堂入室，與女子發生關係。張男食髓知味，一周後又提出類似的要求，結果被對方看到真面目，後者立即致電楊姓男友求救。楊得知後火速趕到高雄，恐嚇並毆打張男，導致他全身多處挫傷。<br />\n<br />\n地檢署處理此案時，認為張男雖假冒女方的男友，使她錯誤獻身，但未以暴力脅迫或違反其意願，因此並不構成強制性交罪；而張與女方發生性關係時，後者並非已婚的狀態，故亦不構成詐術性交。"},{"pid":"ffbc24514f178cee38ac8b7617507b950f4c6590","tid":975697,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:20:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190109/mobile/bkn-20190109171350200-0109_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190109%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190109171350200-0109_00952_001.html&d=oz01qc%2FeAqoMtsiDFJ7X6wKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=cc0273ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190109/mobile/bkn-20190109171350200-0109_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1e9e3ec1505c60fa6c253ec907aea75b1731f08f","tid":975697,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:26:06.000Z","msg":"所以話"},{"pid":"6624548712450ae4a861de3ac1303730b29423c9","tid":975697,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84f397f0ac33b7c361c61dfb1f4fecfc319fa31","tid":975697,"uid":216654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:28:26.000Z","msg":"Birdbox"},{"pid":"a55dcd42a02a8b2f8e593b490b3e5fa1d68e6e1a","tid":975697,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無奇不有"},{"pid":"ac7b9b1266a9f00bd38448f3d9fac62a326da40d","tid":975697,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c26afbb18da7c1d0de055de1ca8246a3816f045","tid":975697,"uid":15406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:31:56.000Z","msg":"寶島"},{"pid":"61bcd1948940d901e277f6fc8520e2fe90900a7e","tid":975697,"uid":91633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f638db365446333ae526050724c14670102297f","tid":975697,"uid":50540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T00:36:15.000Z","msg":"好特別嗎？ 打人斷正，罪成。老強，係難入罪。女方無反抗，男方指蒙眼拐她男友是情趣。點入罪？其實咁樣扮到佢男友都好鬼啦，派帽就派帽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}